Package uk.co.crider.jablus.models.dairy.env

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CowDigestion
    Cow digestion and milk production model, taken from SEPATOU model Objects of this class don't record any internal state other than the outputs produced as a result of executing execDay
    DairyFarm
    Base object to represent the environment.
    Livestock
    Simulates the change in population of cows and bulls on the farm using probabilities of birth and death, along with heard management policy.
    Market
    Encapsulates all economics-based behaviour
    PriceTrend
    Represents the price of a commodity.
    Storage
    Represents a number of stores, each accepting a set of designated item types
